      "text": "Tas Kehninsch no Mado-\nna weens/ tas Kehninsch no A-\nzora weens.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas Kehninsch no Sim-\nron-Merona weens/ tas Keh-\nninsch no Aksapa weens.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas Kehninsch no Taë-\nnaka weens/ tas Kehninsch no\nMegiddus weens.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas Kehninsch no Rahde-\nfa weens/ tas Kehninsch no Jok-\nneana pee Karmela weens.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas Kehninsch no Dora/\nno Nawot-Dora weens/ tas\nKehninsch to Paganu no Gilga-\nla weens.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas Kehninsch no Tir-\nzas weens/ wiſſi tchee Kehnini\nter trithsdeimits un weens.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta XIII. Nodalla.\nStahſti no tahm Tautahm un Semmehm/ kas\nwehl ja-uhſkemm: 1. Josuſs iſdalla us\nDeewa Pauebleſchanutik labbi to uſxeintu\nSemmi/ ka arri to wehl uhſnemmann tahm\npuſſe-mits Ziltim 3. Tas Ibpafchums to\nRuhbena- Gada- un Manaffus Behrnu\nwianpuſſ Zardanas 15/ 24/ 29.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "winun: Tu effi wezz tappis/ u\nlabbt peedſilwojs/ un wel\ntohti dauds Semmes atleek/ ka\nja-uhſkemm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Schi irr ta Semme/ ba\nwehl atleek/ wiſſa Galilea t\nWihtistexu/ un wiſſa Gesure.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "No Siora/ kas preeſch E\ngiptes irr/ lihds tai Ebroxa Roſ\nbeschai prett Seemeli/ kas teer\nKananitexeem peelihdsinata tohp\npeež Yecli-Kungi to Wihtisteru\ntee Gasiteri/ un Asdoditeri/ u\nAskaloniteri/ tee Getiteri/ un Ei\nroniteri/ un Awiteri.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "No Deenas-Widdus Pu-\nfes wiſſa Kananiteru Semme\nun Meara-kas teen Zihdoniteree\npeederr lihds Awekam/ lihds ta\nAmoriteru Rohbeschaf.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ka arri to Gibliteru Sem-\nme/ un wiſſ Lihbanus no Riht-\npuffes/ no Baäl-Gada us appa-\nschu pee ta Ermoza Kalna/ fa\nmehr nahe us Ahmatu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiſſi/ kas Kalnds dſihwo-\nno ta Libbanus lihds teem fulteen\nUhdenim/ wiſſi ZihDoniteri/ es is\ndſihſchu tohs preeſch teem Isra-\netu Behrneem/ peelihdsina tikko\nto Israetam par Ibpafchumu/ it\ntin ka eſteu efmu paweblejs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un nu dalli fcho Semmi\nvar eemantojamu Teeſu tahm de-\nwix Ziltim/ nn tai puff Zilt-\nManaffus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ar to (ohtru puff Zilti) ir-\ntee Rubbeniteri/un Gaditeri jaw-\neemantojamu Teeſu dabbiſcht-\nlo teem Mohsus detve winnpuſ-\nJarda\n"
    }
  ],
